    h1 Navbar React Component
    ul.docs-index
    p Navbar is a fixed (with Fixed and Through layout types) area at the top of a screen that contains Page title and navigation elements.
    p Navbar React component represents <a href="../docs/navbar.html">Navbar</a> component.
    h2 Navbar Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>Navbar</b></code> / <code><b>F7Navbar</b></code>
      li <code><b>NavLeft</b></code> / <code><b>F7NavLeft</b></code>
      li <code><b>NavRight</b></code> / <code><b>F7NavRight</b></code>
      li <code><b>NavTitle</b></code> / <code><b>F7NavTitle</b></code>
