    h2 Navbar Slots
    p Navbar React component (<code>&lt;Navbar&gt;</code>) has additional slots for custom elements:
    ul
      li <code><b>default</b></code> - element will be inserted as a child of <code>&lt;div class="navbar-inner"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>before-inner</b></code> - element will be inserted right before <code>&lt;div class="navbar-inner"&gt;</code> element
      li <code><b>after-inner</b></code> - element will be inserted right after <code>&lt;div class="navbar-inner"&gt;</code> element
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar title="My App">
            <div slot="before-inner">Before Inner</div>
            <div slot="after-inner">After Inner</div>
            <div>Default slot</div>
          </Navbar>

          {/* Renders to: */}

          <div class="navbar">
            <div>Before Inner</div>
            <div class="navbar-inner">
              <div class="title">My App</div>
              <div>Default slot</div>
            </div>
            <div>After Inner</div>
          </div>

    h2 Examples
    h4 Minimal layout
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar title="My App"></Navbar>

    h4 Minimal layout with back link
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar title="My App" backLink="Back"></Navbar>

    h4 Without "sliding" transition effect (affects iOS theme only)
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar title="My App" backLink="Back" sliding="{false}"></Navbar>

    h4 With additional right link to open right panel
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar title="My App" backLink="Back">
            <NavRight>
              <Link icon="icon-bars" panelOpen="right"></Link>
            </NavRight>
          </Navbar>

    h4 All three parts
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar>
            <NavLeft backLink="Back"></NavLeft>
            <NavTitle>My App</NavTitle>
            <NavRight>
              <Link icon="icon-bars" panelOpen="right"></Link>
            </NavRight>
          </Navbar>

    h4 Full custom layout
    :code(lang="jsx")
          <Navbar>
            <NavLeft>
              <Link>Left Link</Link>
            </NavLeft>
            <NavTitle>My App</NavTitle>
            <NavRight>
              <Link>Right Link</Link>
            </NavRight>
          </Navbar>
